    note right of InactiveNoListener
        setActive(true) transitions to ActiveNoListener.
        addDropTargetListener() transitions to InactiveHasListener.
        Drag events (dragEnter, dragOver, etc.) are no-ops when inactive.
    end note

    note right of ActiveHasListener
        addDropTargetListener() throws TooManyListenersException
        (unicast source: only one listener allowed at a time).
        Drag events are forwarded to the registered listener.
    end note

    note right of MaybeActiveListener
        Initial state for parameterized constructors where
        active flag (act) and listener (dtl) cannot be
        statically resolved. setActive() is value-sensitive:
        true -> Active states, false -> Inactive states.
    end note
